column4: …Yes, we did. I was actually waiting for you to come talk about it…
Oh no, I forgot to buy an After Pill! What now?
Ugh... Looks like I will have to accept that she might get pregnant.
I want you to take the pill.""
…Okay. It would be bad for us to have children while in school, afterall.
Yes, I understand. I'll do as you say and take the pill.

column5: I want you to have the baby.""

column4: …Are you sure? You'll have to take responsibility, you know?
Don't worry, I will. Trust me.
Okay~! Would you get mad at me if I said that I was actually hoping for this, a little bit?
Why would I? You're my sweet honeybun.
